name: 塞巴斯蒂安·托里斯
name_full: 塞巴斯蒂安·托里斯 Sebastián Torres
introduction: Sebastián Torres is a Venezuelan actor, writer, director and producer based in Mexico City since 2013. His short films "Job Interview" and "Stupid" have been selected in more than 30 International Film Festivals around the world. He has written five films and several TV series. He is currently developing "Frogman" his first feature film as director.
